transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hi, thank you for calling Viagra. How can I assist you?

Speaker 2: Yeah, I'm trying to cancel my prescription, and you're not allowed to do it online.

Speaker 1: It says you have to call in.

Speaker 2: What's your name and date of birth?

Speaker 1: Patrick Aldrete, 32364.

Speaker 2: Thank you.

Speaker 1: Okay, Patrick, and what's the reason?

Speaker 2: Is it that you have no supply at this time?

Speaker 1: Yeah, I just want to cancel it for now.

Speaker 2: I noticed another charge had gone, so I'm assuming there's another one going.

Speaker 1: I haven't even touched the first one.

Speaker 2: Yeah, so you do have your prescription.

Speaker 1: So what I can go ahead and do for you, if you do not need any at this time,

Speaker 2: is that I can go ahead and just pause your prescription.

Speaker 1: I can pause it for five months, and you can always call to reorder

Speaker 2: if you need any supply before that time.

Speaker 1: Okay, so if I don't – because that's the problem, is if I forget in five months,

Speaker 2: I'm just going to automatically do another –

Speaker 1: There is an email confirmation to let you know when it's about to be time,

Speaker 2: that that time's about to be up.

Speaker 1: And that way you have the option to either extend that pause

Speaker 2: or decide to receive that order.

Speaker 1: Now, will I have to call back in, or am I able to do it online?

Speaker 2: Because it doesn't allow you to do it online.

Speaker 1: I suggest you should give us a call.

Speaker 2: That way you can expect what you're looking for.

Speaker 1: So it's been paused right now.

Speaker 2: The other one, and the one that's already on the way, correct?

Speaker 1: Or is that one cancelled?

Speaker 2: That one is on its way.

Speaker 1: Okay, because I already got the charge, so that's why I wanted to stop it.

Speaker 2: Okay, all righty.

Speaker 1: So you're all set. It's been paused for five months.

Speaker 2: Thank you.

Speaker 1: You're welcome. Have a nice day. Bye.

Speaker 2: You too. Bye.
